@startuml
title Stays4Pilgrims - Suggestions and recommendation communication

actor User
participant "Stays4Pilgrims Frontend" as FE
participant "Stays4Pilgrims Backend" as BE
participant "SuggestionController" as SuggestionController
participant "SuggestionService" as SuggestionService
participant "AccommodationsService" as AccommodationsService
participant "CommentsService" as CommentsService
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "OpenRouter / OpenAI" as AI

User -> FE : open home near current location
FE -> FE : obtain current coordinates and user interest

User -> FE : open nearby suggestions
FE -> BE : POST /sugestoes/sugerir {lat, lon, interesse}
BE -> SuggestionController : sugerir(body)
SuggestionController -> SuggestionService : sugerirLugares(prompt)
SuggestionService -> AI : chat completion with nearby-interest prompt
AI --> SuggestionService : 3 text suggestions
SuggestionService --> BE : text list
BE --> FE : suggestions response
FE --> User : show suggestions notification and dialog

User -> FE : request best accommodation recommendation
FE -> BE : GET /sugestoes/best-accommodation?lat&lon&radius&category
BE -> SuggestionController : bestAccommodation(lat, lon, radius, category)
SuggestionController -> SuggestionService : suggestBestAccommodation(...)
SuggestionService -> AccommodationsService : getByBounds(bounds)
AccommodationsService -> DB : fetch approved accommodations in area
SuggestionService -> CommentsService : use ratings and review counts
CommentsService -> DB : aggregate comment statistics
alt enough local rating data
  SuggestionService -> AI : optional ranking analysis with local options
  AI --> SuggestionService : recommended option or reasoning
else fallback to best local option
  SuggestionService -> SuggestionService : rank by available reviews and ratings
end
SuggestionService --> BE : recommendation + reasoning + alternatives
BE --> FE : JSON recommendation payload
FE --> User : show best accommodation popup

@enduml